## 5. VIỆC CẦN LÀM TIẾP

### ▶ Bước tiếp: Phase 2 E2E Test — Real Backend
**Config đã sẵn sàng** (`USE_MOCK_BACKEND: false`). Chỉ cần:
1. Start Gateway: `docker-compose up -d` trong `layer2_3_gateway/`
2. Health check 3 services
3. Build APK mới (hoặc dùng bản build gần nhất nếu chưa thay code)
4. Test trên physical device theo checklist:

| # | Test Case | Expected |
|---|-----------|----------|
| 2.1 | Health check | "✓ Server connected" trong LoadingScreen |
| 2.2 | L2 done | "✓ Intent analyzed" (có thể fallback vì OpenAI key expired) |
| 2.3 | L3 done | "✓ Found N places" |
| 2.4 | L4 result | "✓ Route optimized — N POIs" |
| 2.5 | Real POI names | Đại Nội, Chùa Thiên Mụ, etc. |
| 2.6 | Tọa độ Huế | lat ~16.4-16.5, lon ~107.5-107.6 |
| 2.7 | Route polyline | Đường phố thực (OSRM) |
| 2.8 | Summary bar | Data khớp itinerary |
| 2.9 | Hotel name | Khớp hotel đã chọn |
| 2.10 | Bug #1 regression | KHÔNG hiển thị mock data |
| 2.11 | Multiple days | Day 1, Day 2 headers |

### ▶ Sau Phase 2: Phase 3 E2E Test — Error + Re-route
| # | Test Case | How to trigger |
|---|-----------|---------------|
| 3.1 | Gateway down | Stop gateway container |
| 3.2 | Empty prompt | Xóa text, tap Next |
| 3.3 | Timeout | Stop L4 while processing |
| 3.4 | Re-route confirm | Tap 🔄 → confirm → GPS → solver |
| 3.5 | Re-route exclude | Uncheck POI → confirm |
| 3.6 | Re-route cancel | Swipe down sheet |
| 3.7 | No GPS | Deny location permission |
| 3.8 | Re-route L4 down | Stop L4 → tap Re-route |

### ▶ Sau E2E: Build APK production
```powershell
$env:EAS_NO_VCS=1; npx eas-cli build --profile preview --platform android --non-interactive
```
> Cần `npx eas-cli login` trước (account: nuyenthang62@gmail.com, đã login).

